OL,3,CCarer and autistic man died in
OL,4,Cfreezing canal while out for a walk
OL,6,FA man with autism and epilepsy drowned
OL,7,Fin a freezing canal alongside his
OL,8,Fcarer while out on a walk, an inquest
OL,9,Fhas heard.
OL,11,FAaron Ritchie and carer Ceri John
OL,12,FJenkins died in the Leeds Liverpool
OL,13,FCanal in November 2023 - but it is
OL,14,Funclear how they came to be in the
OL,15,Fwater.
OL,17,FAn inquest jury, sitting at Bolton
OL,18,FCoroner's Court, is now examining the
OL,19,Fcircumstances surrounding their deaths.
