OL,3,CCarer and autistic man died in
OL,4,Cfreezing canal while out for a walk
OL,6,FMr Ritchie, 49, who the jury heard had
OL,7,Fa mental age of 10 or less, was a long-
OL,8,Fterm resident of Mayfield House care
OL,9,Fhome in Wigan, while Oxford University-
OL,10,Feducated Mr Jenkins was his care
OL,11,Fworker on the day.
OL,13,FThe inquest was told the pair were
OL,14,Fwalking along the towpath, in the
OL,15,FAbram area of Wigan, near Crankwood
OL,16,FRoad - one of Mr Ritchie's favourite
OL,17,Fwalks, there was then a brief 15-
OL,18,Fminute window when they were last seen
OL,19,Fto when witnesses then spotted them in
OL,20,Fthe water.
