OL,4,Cfreezing canal while out for a walk
OL,6,FCoroner Timothy Brennand said there
OL,7,Fwas an absence of direct evidence and
OL,8,Fit was not known who entered the water
OL,9,Ffirst.
OL,11,FHowever, Lorraine Jenkins, Mr Jenkins
OL,12,Fwidow, said if Mr Ritchie had fallen
OL,13,Finto the water first his "focus would
OL,14,Fhave been on him".
OL,16,FIn a statement referenced by the
OL,17,Fcoroner she said: "It would be
OL,18,Fcompletely Aaron on his mind.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/11
