OL,3,CCarer and autistic man died in
OL,4,Cfreezing canal while out for a walk
OL,6,F"He was the best and most loving
OL,7,Fhusband I could have."
OL,9,FMr Jenkins had been a support worker
OL,10,Fat Mayfield House since November 2020,
OL,11,Fhe was described by his widow as
OL,12,F"extremely vigilant".
OL,14,F"He loved it and felt like he could
OL,15,Fmake a difference," she said.
OL,17,F"He wanted (the residents) to have
OL,18,Ffulfilling lives and he went above and
OL,19,Fbeyond. He loved them all and had time
OL,20,Ffor all of them.
