OL,3,CCarer and autistic man died in
OL,4,Cfreezing canal while out for a walk
OL,6,FHe often walked on tiptoes and would
OL,7,Fsometimes 'burst' into skips and
OL,8,Frunning, the jury heard. The frequency
OL,9,Fof his seizures - said to be several a
OL,10,Fday - meant he had one-to-one care.
OL,12,FMr Ritchie's cause of death was given
OL,13,Fas "cold water drowning" after a post-
OL,14,Fmortem examination, the court heard.
OL,16,FPathologist Dr Patrick Waugh said he
OL,17,Fwas not left alone at any time due to
OL,18,Fhis frequent seizures but whether or
OL,19,Fnot he had experienced a seizure at
OL,20,Fthe time could not be resolved by
OL,21,Fpathology, he said.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/11
