OL,3,CCarer and autistic man died in
OL,4,Cfreezing canal while out for a walk
OL,6,FCold water, Dr Waugh said, on what was
OL,7,Fa winter's day, was a factor in the
OL,8,Fcase. "I do not know whether he was
OL,9,Fhaving a seizure at the time," he
OL,10,Fadded. "There is always caution
OL,11,Fexercised around water with people
OL,12,Fwith epilepsy."
OL,14,FMr Jenkins' cause of death was given
OL,15,Fas drowning.
OL,17,FMr Ritchie's aunt, Jacqueline
OL,18,FDarbyshire, said he could not
OL,19,Fcommunicate normally and required
OL,20,Fsupported accommodation at the home
OL,21,Ffrom 2007.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/11
